This directory (src) contains the KIM API routines and related files.

The contents of the directory are as follows (before any compilation is
performed):

KIM_API.cpp
     C++ implementations of core library routines and methods.

KIM_API.h
     C++ Header file for KIM API library classes, routines and methods.

KIM_API_C.cpp
     Implementation of C-style interface for the KIM API.

KIM_API_C.h
     Header for C-style interface of KIM API library routines.

KIM_API_DIRS.cpp
     C++ implementation file containing library directory lookup routine (for
     "in-place" and "installed" use of the KIM API library).

KIM_API_DIRS.h
     Header file defining a routine to supply directory locations to be searched
     by the KIM API.

KIM_API_F03.F03
     Implementation of Fortran 2003-style interface for KIM API library.

KIM_API_F03_Helper.F03
     Implementation of helper routines for the Fortran 2003-style interface.

KIM_API_Version.h.tpl
     Template file from which the KIM_API_Version.h header file is created.

KIM_API_status.h
     Header file defining the KIM API status codes.

KIM_AUX.cpp
     C++ implementation file containing auxiliary routines, including
     the native process_dEdr and process_d2Edr2 functions.

KIM_AUX.h
     Header file declaring the auxiliary routines.

Makefile
     Make file for building the KIM API library.

README
     This file.

Unit_Handling.cpp
     C++ implementation file defining the unit handling capabilities of the KIM
     API.

Unit_Handling.h
     Header file declaring the unit handling functions.

scripts/
     Directory containing helper scripts for building the KIM API.

standard.kim
     KIM descriptor file with definition and description of all standard
     arguments.

utils/
     Directory containing code for various helper binaries distributed with the
     KIM API.
